  "turns": [
    {
      "global_turn_index": 1,
      "scene_index": 1,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_01.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_01_news_context",
      "section_title": "section_01",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "觀眾朋友大家好，歡迎收看本週的總經瞭望。Miranda，這個禮拜市場訊息感覺相當分歧。一方面，我們看到 Fed 會議紀錄提到，不排除把升息重新納入選項；但另一方面，又有美伊和平協議的傳聞，讓油價出現了明顯回落。",
      "subtitle_text": "本週市場訊息分歧：Fed鷹派 vs. 油價回落",
      "estimated_seconds": 20.0,
      "segment_index": 1,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_000_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 0.0,
      "duration_sec": 13.968,
      "end_sec": 13.968
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 2,
      "scene_index": 1,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_01.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_01_news_context",
      "section_title": "section_01",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "Tom 說的沒錯，這就是本週的複雜之處。市場不再交易單一的劇本。我們看到，西德州原油（WTI）價格從週初的 105 美元附近，一路下跌到 97 美元左右，這照理說應該會緩解通膨擔憂。",
      "subtitle_text": "油價顯著回落，從105美元跌至97美元",
      "estimated_seconds": 16.0,
      "segment_index": 2,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_001_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 13.968,
      "duration_sec": 42.816,
      "end_sec": 56.784
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 3,
      "scene_index": 1,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_01.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_01_news_context",
      "section_title": "section_01",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "但奇怪的是，攸關市場利率的美國十年期公債殖利率，卻沒有跟著油價一起放鬆。它整週幾乎都維持在 4.6% 上下的高檔，甚至三十年期殖利率還創了 19 年新高。這兩者之間似乎出現了脫鉤。",
      "subtitle_text": "但美債殖利率維持高檔，並未隨油價放鬆",
      "estimated_seconds": 18.0,
      "segment_index": 3,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_002_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 56.784,
      "duration_sec": 16.176,
      "end_sec": 72.96
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 4,
      "scene_index": 1,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_01.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_01_news_context",
      "section_title": "section_01",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "是的，這個脫鉤就是本週的關鍵。市場價格驗證了新聞中的分歧點。除了 Fed 的鷹派訊號，還有房市數據疲軟帶來的成長擔憂。這些力量交錯在一起，導致美元指數雖然強勢，卻是在高位震盪，而亞洲貨幣則普遍承壓。",
      "subtitle_text": "市場價格驗證了新聞中的分歧點",
      "estimated_seconds": 20.0,
      "segment_index": 4,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_003_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 72.96,
      "duration_sec": 33.552,
      "end_sec": 106.512
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 5,
      "scene_index": 1,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_01.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_01_news_context",
      "section_title": "section_01",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "所以，油價下跌的利多，似乎被其他因素抵銷了。既然如此，我們首先應該來釐清，在這些互相矛盾的訊號之下，市場對於通膨的預期，到底有沒有形成一個明確的方向？",
      "subtitle_text": "通膨預期是否已形成明確方向？",
      "estimated_seconds": 14.0,
      "segment_index": 5,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_004_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 106.512,
      "duration_sec": 9.216,
      "end_sec": 115.728
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 6,
      "scene_index": 2,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_02.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_02_inflation_expectation",
      "section_title": "section_02",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "這個問題非常好。目前市場對通膨的預期，我會用「訊號交錯」來形容。一方面，我們不能忘記四月份的 CPI 年增還有 3.8%，PPI 更一度高達 6%，這為通膨的黏固性提供了很強的背景證據。",
      "subtitle_text": "通膨預期呈現「訊號交錯」的狀態",
      "estimated_seconds": 19.0,
      "segment_index": 6,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_005_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 115.728,
      "duration_sec": 18.0,
      "end_sec": 133.728
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 7,
      "scene_index": 2,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_02.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_02_inflation_expectation",
      "section_title": "section_02",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "這確實是先前市場非常擔憂的數據，也是「高利率維持更久」這個論述的主要支撐。但本週油價的下跌，難道沒有改變這個預期嗎？畢竟能源價格是通膨一個很重要的組成部分。",
      "subtitle_text": "油價下跌是否改變了高通膨預期？",
      "estimated_seconds": 16.0,
      "segment_index": 7,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_006_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 133.728,
      "duration_sec": 19.08,
      "end_sec": 152.808
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 8,
      "scene_index": 2,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_02.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_02_inflation_expectation",
      "section_title": "section_02",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "它確實帶來了修正，但還不足以完全扭轉。油價因為美伊和平的曙光而顯著走跌，讓能源端的通膨壓力短期內出現了緩解。但這是一個地緣政治事件，隨時可能反轉。所以市場的看法是，一個潛在的利多出現了，但還不能完全抵銷先前累積的通膨數據壓力。",
      "subtitle_text": "油價下跌帶來修正，但未完全扭轉預期",
      "estimated_seconds": 23.0,
      "segment_index": 8,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_007_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 152.808,
      "duration_sec": 40.392,
      "end_sec": 193.2
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 9,
      "scene_index": 2,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_02.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_02_inflation_expectation",
      "section_title": "section_02",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "我明白了。所以並不是市場沒看到油價下跌，而是它選擇更謹慎地評估，認為目前還沒有形成一個通膨確定會降溫的單一方向。但這就帶來下一個問題了，如果通膨訊號只是分歧，為什麼利率市場的反應看起來還是這麼偏向鷹派呢？",
      "subtitle_text": "若通膨訊號分歧，為何利率反應偏鷹派？",
      "estimated_seconds": 22.0,
      "segment_index": 9,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_008_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 193.2,
      "duration_sec": 17.328,
      "end_sec": 210.528
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 10,
      "scene_index": 3,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_03.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_03_rate_driver",
      "section_title": "section_03",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "利率維持高檔，並非只看通膨。本週有三個關鍵的驅動因素。第一，也是最重要的，就是 Fed 的政策訊號。會議紀錄直接表明，多數官員認為應該保留升息的選項，這等於是直接對市場的降息預期潑了一盆冷水。",
      "subtitle_text": "利率驅動因素一：Fed的鷹派政策訊號",
      "estimated_seconds": 21.0,
      "segment_index": 10,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_009_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 210.528,
      "duration_sec": 32.232,
      "end_sec": 242.76
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 11,
      "scene_index": 3,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_03.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_03_rate_driver",
      "section_title": "section_03",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "第二，就是我們剛才提到的，前期強勁的通膨數據，它仍然是利率維持高檔的基本面支撐。第三個因素比較結構性，是來自長天期債券。三十年期美債殖利率突破 5.1%，創下 19 年新高，這代表市場正在重新評估持有長期債券的風險，要求更高的「期限溢價」。",
      "subtitle_text": "因素二與三：通膨數據與長債期限溢價",
      "estimated_seconds": 26.0,
      "segment_index": 11,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_010_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 242.76,
      "duration_sec": 10.32,
      "end_sec": 253.08
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 12,
      "scene_index": 3,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_03.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_03_rate_driver",
      "section_title": "section_03",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "所以，即使本週的油價下跌，也難以撼動這三大支柱。不過，我們也看到房市數據相當疲軟，這難道沒有對利率產生一些向下的拉力嗎？",
      "subtitle_text": "房市數據疲軟是否對利率產生影響？",
      "estimated_seconds": 13.0,
      "segment_index": 12,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_011_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 253.08,
      "duration_sec": 12.576,
      "end_sec": 265.656
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 13,
      "scene_index": 3,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_03.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_03_rate_driver",
      "section_title": "section_03",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "有，這就是為什麼十年期殖利率沒有一路向上突破的原因。它在本週呈現一個倒V型的走勢，週初上攻，但碰到房市數據疲軟引發的成長擔憂後就回落了。這股抵銷力量讓利率最終呈現高位震盪，而不是單邊上行。",
      "subtitle_text": "成長擔憂形成抵銷，利率呈現高位震盪",
      "estimated_seconds": 20.0,
      "segment_index": 13,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_012_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 265.656,
      "duration_sec": 13.848,
      "end_sec": 279.504
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 14,
      "scene_index": 3,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_03.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_03_rate_driver",
      "section_title": "section_03",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "了解了，所以利率市場是鷹派政策和成長擔憂兩種力量的平衡結果。那麼在這樣一個高利率維持的環境下，市場對於美元和黃金這兩大資產，又是如何重新定價的呢？",
      "subtitle_text": "高利率環境下，美元與黃金如何定價？",
      "estimated_seconds": 15.0,
      "segment_index": 14,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_013_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 279.504,
      "duration_sec": 38.28,
      "end_sec": 317.784
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 15,
      "scene_index": 4,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_04.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_04_dollar_gold",
      "section_title": "section_04",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "在高利率環境下，美元的利差優勢非常明顯，這是支撐美元指數維持在 99 上方高位區間的核心動力。簡單說，資金停泊在美元能賺取更高的利息。",
      "subtitle_text": "高利率環境確立美元的利差優勢",
      "estimated_seconds": 15.0,
      "segment_index": 15,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_014_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 317.784,
      "duration_sec": 17.952,
      "end_sec": 335.736
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 16,
      "scene_index": 4,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_04.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_04_dollar_gold",
      "section_title": "section_04",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "但我們也看到美元指數並不是一路向上，而是在一個區間內震盪。這是否也跟我們剛才提到的成長擔憂有關？",
      "subtitle_text": "美元高位震盪，受成長擔憂限制",
      "estimated_seconds": 11.0,
      "segment_index": 16,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_015_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 335.736,
      "duration_sec": 37.632,
      "end_sec": 373.368
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 17,
      "scene_index": 4,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_04.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_04_dollar_gold",
      "section_title": "section_04",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "完全正確。經濟硬著陸的擔憂，限制了美元進一步上漲的空間。所以美元的狀態是「偏強，但受干擾」。至於黃金，它的處境就更加矛盾。一方面，高利率等於提高了持有黃金這種零孳息資產的機會成本，對金價是壓力。",
      "subtitle_text": "黃金處境矛盾：高利率形成機會成本",
      "estimated_seconds": 21.0,
      "segment_index": 17,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_016_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 373.368,
      "duration_sec": 16.296,
      "end_sec": 389.664
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 18,
      "scene_index": 4,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_04.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_04_dollar_gold",
      "section_title": "section_04",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "但另一方面，不論是美伊談判的地緣政治風險，還是房市疲軟引發的成長放緩擔憂，都激發了市場的避險需求，這對黃金又是支撐。所以我們看到金價本週上沖下洗，在 4480 到 4577 美元之間寬幅震盪，這就是兩股力量拉扯的結果。",
      "subtitle_text": "避險需求形成支撐，金價寬幅震盪",
      "estimated_seconds": 22.0,
      "segment_index": 18,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_017_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 389.664,
      "duration_sec": 20.4,
      "end_sec": 410.064
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 19,
      "scene_index": 4,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_04.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_04_dollar_gold",
      "section_title": "section_04",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "原來如此，所以美元和黃金看似都強，但背後的驅動因素不完全相同。美元主要靠利差，黃金則靠避險。那麼，在美元維持強勢的大格局下，亞洲主要貨幣又承受了什麼樣的壓力呢？",
      "subtitle_text": "強美元格局下，亞洲貨幣壓力為何？",
      "estimated_seconds": 16.0,
      "segment_index": 19,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_018_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 410.064,
      "duration_sec": 16.32,
      "end_sec": 426.384
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 20,
      "scene_index": 5,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_05.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_05_asia_fx",
      "section_title": "section_05",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "亞洲貨幣可以說是全面承受壓力。首先看日圓，美日之間的巨大利差，讓日圓的貶值壓力最為顯著，美元兌日圓一度逼近 159 的高位，幾乎沒有任何實質性的支撐。",
      "subtitle_text": "日圓因巨大利差，承受最顯著貶值壓力",
      "estimated_seconds": 16.0,
      "segment_index": 20,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_019_Miranda.mp3",
      "start_sec": 426.384,
      "duration_sec": 48.264,
      "end_sec": 474.648
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 21,
      "scene_index": 5,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_05.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_05_asia_fx",
      "section_title": "section_05",
      "speaker": "Tom",
      "spoken_text": "韓圜的狀況似乎也很嚴峻，我看到美元兌韓圜甚至升破了 1500 這個重要的心理關卡。",
      "subtitle_text": "韓圜同樣嚴峻，美元兌韓圜升破1500",
      "estimated_seconds": 9.0,
      "segment_index": 21,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_020_Tom.mp3",
      "start_sec": 474.648,
      "duration_sec": 17.712,
      "end_sec": 492.36
    },
    {
      "global_turn_index": 22,
      "scene_index": 5,
      "scene_image": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_visual_images/scene_05.jpg",
      "section_id": "scene_05_asia_fx",
      "section_title": "section_05",
      "speaker": "Miranda",
      "spoken_text": "是的，韓圜除了受到強美元衝擊，也對全球貿易和經濟成長的擔憂特別敏感，所以承受的是雙重壓力。至於新台幣，同樣面臨台美利差擴大和外資動向的壓力，美元兌台幣一度貶到 31.64，雖然之後略有回落，但整體貶值的壓力格局沒有改變。",
      "subtitle_text": "韓圜與台幣同樣面臨貶值壓力",
      "estimated_seconds": 23.0,
      "segment_index": 22,
      "segment_audio": "output/weekly/2026-05-21/story_audio/segments/seg_021_Miranda.mp3",
